data.description: Welcome to your dream home! 7671 Hwy 300 offers high ceilings throughout, copper ceilings in the master bathroom and one guest bedroom, beautiful crown molding, a spacious and open gourmet kitchen, great split floorplan, outdoor paradise with a huge backyard. Step into your private oasis and unwind in the luxurious gunite pool. Designed to impress, this pool is constructed with durable and versatile gunite material, ensuring years of enjoyment. Whether it's a refreshing morning swim or an evening poolside gathering with friends, this pool is the epitome of relaxation and entertainment. This energy efficient 3/2/2 home also has 1-year-old SOLAR PANELS! Embrace sustainable living with the solar panels installed on this property. Enjoy the benefits of reduced electricity bills while minimizing your carbon footprint. These eco-friendly panels harness the sun's energy, powering your home and helping you contribute to a greener planet. Convenient to both Longview and Gilmer, and in Gilmer ISD. Don't miss the chance to make 7671 Hwy 300 your forever home. Schedule a private tour today! *Buyer must also qualify for solar loan*
